HOT GIRL SUMMER GIVEAWAY 🌸

Win: 1 TAN + LINES bikini of your choice, 1 TAN + LINES bikini bag, 1 TAN + LINES muse towel, 1 $200 gift card to Winc & 1 $200 gift card to Funboy!

To enter: 
1. Like this post
2. Follow all three: @shoptanlines @funboy @winc
3. Tag a friend in the comments
You can enter as many times as you like (just be sure to tag a different friend each time!). Winner will be picked on 7/29 at 10am PST. Profile must be public to enter.
Legal stuff: 
Must be 21+ to enter and a U.S. resident
Gift card from Winc is exclusive of tax and shipping
Winc cannot ship wine to: AL, AK, AR, DE, HI, KY, MI, MS, NJ, RH, SD and UT

node.text:
SUMMER ESSENTIALS GIFTAWAY! ⛱Celebrate summer with the necessities you need to make it great. We've teamed up with our friends at @gigicbikinis , @everedenbrand, and @tower28beauty to set you up this season.

What you'll win:
The GIGI C Georgia Top and Jaclyn Bottom in White from @gigicbikinis
The Vintage Cali Towel from @funboy
The Sheer Botanical Facial Sunscreen SPF30
from @everedenbrand
The SOS Daily Rescue Facial Spray & Bronzino Illuminating Cream Bronzer from @tower28beauty

To enter:
Follow all accounts
Tag 2 friends in the comments
Enter email in link: https://gigicbikinis.com/pages/summer-giftaway
Giftaway ends Saturday, July 24th at 11:59PM PST. Valid for North American residents only. This giftaway is not sponsored by Instagram. Good luck! 💖🌸
